# NewsApp

iOS News Application with AppStore-style Search.

## Features

- Tab bar search
- Empty state
- API based search
- Bookmark & Newsfeed style UI
- Dark mode support
- Unit tests included

## Tech Stack

- Swift
- UIKit / SwiftUI
- MVVM
- URLSession

## How to Run

1. Clone repo
2. Open .xcodeproj
3. Run on simulator
